<br />
Here's the same list, with the lowest prices I was able to find in the Torvon server bazaar.  N/A indicates it wasn't on sale this afternoon.  I'll edit the post as I find prices tonight or this week.
<br />

<br />
Updated thrice - still haven't found a number of them.
<br />

<br />
Barnacle Covered Axe - Pique (Increased Hate) - 100pp
<br />
Blackhand Berserker's Axe - Shieldskin - 75pp - does not actually use a cat's eye (thanks Mileron)
<br />
Fury Edged Short Sword - Shock of Swords - N/A
<br />
Jeldorin - Knight's Blessing (180 hp heal) - N/A
<br />
Obtenebrate Short Sword - Dooming Darkness - 250pp
<br />
Kicsh Der Pavz - Strong Poison - N/A
<br />
Polished Obsidian Tomahawk - 200 dmg absorb - N/A
<br />
Silken Whip of Ensnaring - Snare - N/A
<br />
Silver Blade of Thunder - Thunder Strike 263 DD+0 second stun - N/A
<br />
Sword of Skyfire - Rain of Fire - 5000pp
<br />
Sword of the Morning - Tishan's Clash 50 DD+5 second stun - 3700pp
<br />
Adamantite Club - Stunning Blow 60 DD+6 second stun (might be nice combo with sword of the morning.)  - 400pp
<br />
Anklesmasher - Snare - N/A
<br />
Baton of Royal Stature - Stunning Blow - N/A
<br />
Bottle of Gelatinous Slime - Inferno Shock - N/A
<br />
DawnFire, Morning Star of Light - Banish Undead (CoD anyone?) - 1000pp
<br />
Dedgerex's Flintforged Cudgel - Conflagration - N/A
<br />
Delightful Orb of Forgotten Magic - Ice Shock - 8000pp
<br />
Incandescent Wand - 6 second PBAE stun - N/A
<br />
Sarnak Devastator - Holy Might, 60 DD, 6 second stun - N/A
<br />
Writ of Di`zok - 65% slow - N/A
<br />
Harmonic Dagger - Tishan's Clash 50DD+5 sec stun - 1000pp (thx Zacatac)
<br />
Lupine Dagger - Greater Wolf Form (go go wolf pet, nice atk boost) - 5000pp
<br />
Sarnak Summoner's Dagger - Blaze - 1000pp
<br />
Steel Hilted Flint Dagger - Conflagration UBAH proc - 3000pp
<br />

<br />
A lot of ones I couldn't find so far.  Like I said, I'll update.  Prices may vary in your area and are succeptible to local tax and penalties.
<br />

<br />
Some thoughts so far 
<br />

<br />
- dawnfire sounds awesome for CoD!  Plus it's not lore!
<br />

<br />
- Lupine dagger would be fun as hell, if you have the cash...
<br />

<br />
- The Lore tagged items aren't too big a deal if you've got a friend, just have each of you carry one and hand them both to the pet, since it ignores Lore.  Two adamantite clubs with WoX would be stun-tastic!
<br />

<br />
- It's still gonna be hard to beat the di'zok oracle shillelagh for one of the two slots, or even both slots for faster effect.
<br />

<br />
- Heal or damage-absorb procs might be better than siphon-types, as they don't require a save.  My experience with Bloodpoint (80 hp steal) doesn't give me a lot of hope for either though.
<br />

<br />
- Anyone know one handers with fear effect?  Servant of Marr + two fear weapons would make the necros jealous!!  Or maybe toss a snare proc in one slot to minimize run distance.
<br />

<br />
Today's thoughts,
<br />
-Dretchulos
